claim.claim-text:
A method for recording and playing a user voice in a mobile terminal, the method comprising:
entering a page by executing an electronic book;
identifying whether a user voice record file related to the page exists;
generating a user voice record file related to the page by recording a text included in the page to a user voice if the user voice record file does not exist; and
playing by synchronizing the user voice stored in the user voice record file with the text if the user voice record file exists.
